            p.ta-c You can say #[strong ‘excuse me’]  in order to get the person’s attention.
            p.ta-c #[strong ‘Could’] is also a polite way to request something.
            .row
                .col.xs12.md8.col-center
                    .row-flex.mt30.flex.align-items-center.mt20.justify-around
                        button(class="c-btn-IconAction u-bgIconListen mr10" ng-audio="unit_2/module_8/assets/audios/act_12_1.mp3")
                        button(class="c-btn-IconAction u-bgIconListen mr10" ng-audio="unit_2/module_8/assets/audios/act_12_2.mp3")
