            .row.mt30
                h5 #[strong Embarrassment]#[br]
                p.
                    Expressing embarrassment is expressing how ashamed one is of or for doing something. #[br]
                    Here are few expressions:
            div(class="row row-flex align-items-center justify-center")
                .col.xs12.md5
                    .c-cardGreen
                        .c-cardGreenContent.u-textColor_1
                            p.
                                #[strong Embarrassment] tends to refer to#[strong  socially awkward or uncomfortable contexts].#[br]#[br]
                                • feel / be (so) embarrassed when / because + explanation#[br]
                                • feel / be (so) embarrassed to + verb#[br]
                                • make someone feel ashamed / embarrassed#[br]
                            div(class="row"): div(class="row row-flex align-items-center justify-center")
                                .col.xs6.sm4.md6.mt20: div(class="row row-flex align-items-center justify-center")
